* Thoory ( Thuri ) – popular in Algeria , this dry date is brown - red when cured with a bluish bloom and very wrinkled skin .
Its flesh is sometimes hard and brittle but the flavour described as sweet and nutty .
* Umeljwary – in Libya .
* Umelkhashab – Brilliant red skin ; bittersweet , hard white flesh ( Saudi Arabia ) .
